  <p>
    <a href="/disc-stack-centrifuge/">Looking for a complete turnkey system? See our disc stack centrifuge systems &rarr;</a>
  </p>

  <details class="border-l-4 border-gold/40 pl-4 mb-3 group">
    <summary class="cursor-pointer font-semibold text-navy py-2 list-none flex justify-between items-center">
      What is the Dolphin equivalent of the Alfa Laval WHPX 510?
      <span class="text-gold ml-2 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">&#9660;</span>
    </summary>
    <p class="text-text-light mt-2 pb-2">The Dolphin DMPX-042 centrifuge system is built around the Alfa Laval WHPX 510 (or equivalent MOPX 209/310 / MAPX 210) centrifuge bowl. The DMPX-042 is a complete system module rated at 32–47 GPM on diesel, with full PLC controls, electric heaters, and piping.</p>
  </details>
  <details class="border-l-4 border-gold/40 pl-4 mb-3 group">
    <summary class="cursor-pointer font-semibold text-navy py-2 list-none flex justify-between items-center">
      What flow rate does the Alfa Laval WHPX 510 handle?
      <span class="text-gold ml-2 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">&#9660;</span>
    </summary>
    <p class="text-text-light mt-2 pb-2">The Alfa Laval WHPX 510 handles approximately 42 GPM on diesel fuel (13 cSt at operating temperature) and approximately 24 GPM on lube oil at 30 cSt. For the equivalent Dolphin DMPX-042 system, rated capacity ranges from 32 to 47 GPM on diesel depending on configuration.</p>
  </details>
  <details class="border-l-4 border-gold/40 pl-4 mb-3 group">
    <summary class="cursor-pointer font-semibold text-navy py-2 list-none flex justify-between items-center">
      Is the WHPX 510 self-cleaning or manual clean?
      <span class="text-gold ml-2 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">&#9660;</span>
    </summary>
    <p class="text-text-light mt-2 pb-2">The Alfa Laval WHPX 510 is a self-cleaning (automatic partial-discharge) disc stack centrifuge. The bowl automatically ejects accumulated sludge through timed discharge cycles without stopping the centrifuge. This allows continuous uninterrupted operation ideal for high-volume waste oil and diesel purification applications.</p>
  </details>
  <details class="border-l-4 border-gold/40 pl-4 mb-3 group">
    <summary class="cursor-pointer font-semibold text-navy py-2 list-none flex justify-between items-center">
      What industries use the WHPX 510 / DMPX-042 centrifuge?
      <span class="text-gold ml-2 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">&#9660;</span>
    </summary>
    <p class="text-text-light mt-2 pb-2">The WHPX 510 / DMPX-042 is widely used in: waste oil recovery and re-refining, diesel fuel polishing for large fleet operations, crude oil dehydration in oilfields, biodiesel glycerin separation, marine fuel purification, and industrial lube oil reclamation. Its 42 GPM capacity on diesel makes it one of the most popular mid-range industrial centrifuges.</p>
  </details>
  <details class="border-l-4 border-gold/40 pl-4 mb-3 group">
    <summary class="cursor-pointer font-semibold text-navy py-2 list-none flex justify-between items-center">
      Can Dolphin Centrifuge supply parts or rebuild the WHPX 510?
      <span class="text-gold ml-2 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">&#9660;</span>
    </summary>
    <p class="text-text-light mt-2 pb-2">Yes. Dolphin Centrifuge supplies genuine and compatible replacement parts for the WHPX 510, including disc stacks, seals, bearings, and discharge valve components. Complete bowl rebuilds and remanufactured WHPX 510 centrifuges are available. Each rebuilt unit is factory tested before shipment.</p>
  </details>

  <div class="bg-navy rounded-xl p-8 text-center mt-12 not-prose">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Parts, Repairs &amp; Remanufactured WHPX 510</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6 max-w-lg mx-auto">Contact Dolphin Centrifuge for pricing, availability, and application support. Free sample testing available for qualifying applications.</p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3">
      <a href="/contact-for-alfa-laval-centrifuges/" class="bg-gold hover:bg-gold/80 text-navy font-bold px-8 py-3 rounded-lg transition-colors">Get a Quote</a>
      <a href="/industrial-centrifuge-sample-testing/" class="border border-white/30 hover:border-gold text-white font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-lg transition-colors">Free Sample Testing</a>
      <a href="tel:+12485222573" class="border border-white/30 hover:border-gold text-white font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-lg transition-colors">(248) 522-2573</a>
    </div>
  </div>

</ApplicationLayout>
